  m_text: 'Diamond Riches is a 3x3, 10 line video slot featuring Diamond Payouts
    and Unlimited Free Spins This game has a fixed number of 10 paylines, you cannot
    change the number of active paylines.

    Changing the bet amount automatically
    changes the win amounts displayed in the paytable, those amounts are displayed
    in the currency you selected.

