  m_text: 'When identical matching symbols appear consecutively on an active payline
    from left to right, you win(see paytable for more details).

    Only the highest
    win on an active payline will be paid.

    If you have more than one win on
    a single spin, the total amount of your winnings is added together, displayed
    in the win field and added to your balance.'
